                  , and was employed and entrusted by him to receive money for him, and that being such servant, so employed and entrusted, did receive and take into his possession the sum of 33 l. 9 s. 9 d. and that he afterwards did secrete and steal 15 l. 9 s. 9 d. part of the said sum
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>SECOND COUNT, for secreting the said sum, stating that he received it of 
